{"type":null,"faqId":10511,"title":"P6-U06  彩信","answer":"<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span>1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">发送彩信\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">进入消息菜单，选择<b>新信息</b>，撰写新信息；</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">输入收件人和编辑消息内容；</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">按菜单键，再选择<b>添加主题</b>（添加主题后自动转换为彩信）；</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点击文本框左边按钮添加附件，可以加入图片、音频或视频（添加多媒体文件自动转成彩信）；</span> \n\t</p>\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31687\" alt=\"\" /> \n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">编辑完成后，点击<b>发送</b>。</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t\t<span>2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">彩信发送</span><span>/</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">接收失败的可能原因，解决方法</span> \n\t</h3>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:黑体;\"></span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">网络繁忙或信号不好时，会导致彩信发送失败。</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">通俗说法：由于网络侧繁忙或信号不好等原因，不能处理发送彩信。导致发送失败。</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">解决方法：稍后重试发送。</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">被网络侧（彩信中心）拒绝时，会导致彩信发送失败。</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">通俗说法</span><span>1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">：收件人号码信息填写不正确，导致发送失败。</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">解决方法</span><span>1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">：检查收件人号码是否正确，如果错误，请更正后，重发彩信。</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">通俗说法</span><span>2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">：编辑的彩信超过了</span><span>300KB</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，导致不能发送。</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">解决方法</span><span>2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">：删除一些彩信内容，另彩信小于</span><span>300KB</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，再尝试发送。</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">是否欠费了。</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">通俗说法：欠费导致发送失败。</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">解决方法：缴费后，重新发送。</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">手机内存不足时，无法接收彩信</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">通俗说法：欠费导致发送失败。</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">解决方法：释放手机内存，使剩余空间大于</span><span>300K</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span> \n\t</p>\n\t<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">3.彩信是否受文件大小</span><span>/</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">视频格式</span><span>/</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">分辨率等因素限制\n\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n\t\t\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">视频和音频文件超过规定大小（通常是</span><span>300k</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）则无法添加为附件。图片文件过大时会自动压缩图片分辨率，再以附件添加到彩信中，接收方收到的图片文件也是低分辨率的图片。</span> \n\t\t</p>\n\t\t<h3 style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t\t\t<span>4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:黑体;\">彩信的附件保存位置</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:宋体;\"></span> \n\t\t</h3>\n\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">用到彩信后，彩信的附件是存在</span><span>/data </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">路径下，用户不可见。</span> \n\t\t</p>\n\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">当用户将附件保存后，附件的存储位置为：</span> \n\t\t</p>\n\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">手机内部存储</span><span>/storage/emulated/0/DCIM/Camera</span> \n\t\t</p>\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31688\" alt=\"\" /></span> \n\t</h3>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:黑体;\"><br />\n</span> \n\t</p>\n<br />\n</span> \n\t<p>\n\t\t<br />\n\t</p>\n<br />\n</h3>","faqTypeId":136,"faqType":"信息与邮件","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1236","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-SMS-Email","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1397630739000,"seriesProductName":"EDGE-U00","visitedTimes":32,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}